review_blob:
Fantastic! Finally a beer I can enjoy in the finest of company! The company of Gentlemen, that is!

Hear Ye Hear Ye!

Nothing says "kicks" better than a billiard table, my closest and most private gentleman friends and a case of beer that tastes so awful youll forget how bad it smells.

If the stench doesnt kill you, the retina-burning sky blue/pastel yellow color scheme will induce an eplieptic seizure.

The Private Mens Club approves!!!

"By the hair on my lip, a fine pilsner!"
               -R.Finnius Blackinton III
